title: Till Sofia
info:
#bermuda triangle#
presents
a tune to the very
nicest person Minthy!
made especially for
her :)

greets to all the peo-
ple giving their best
friendship to this
wonderful person :))

notice: the refrain is
an almost total ripoff
of Erasure. The smp-
set was taken directly
from the tune:
"She Came To Me"

Pleez, don't spread
this tune! :)
